'''Victoria Mixon''' is an [[Americans|American]] [[Editor#Editing services|independent fiction editor]] and writer. She was co-author of the first published book on introducing children to the Internet, and has written two books on the craft of writing fiction.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thebookdesigner.com/2011/10/victoria-mixon-bang/|title=Writers: How to Open With a Bang!|last=Friedlander|first=Joel|date=5 October 2011|publisher=The Book Designer|accessdate=30 September 2014}}</ref>

