* {{cite book |title= The Art & Craft of Writing Fiction: 1st Practitioner's Manual |date= 2010 |publisher= La Favorita Press |isbn= 9780984542703}}
* {{cite book |title= The Art & Craft of Writing Stories: 2nd Practitioner's Manual |date= 2011 |publisher= La Favorita Press |isbn= 9780984542734}}
* {{cite book |title= The Art & Craft of Writing: Secret Advice for Writers |date= 2015 |publisher= La Favorita Press |isbn= 9781994227043|ignore-isbn-error=true}}
* {{cite book |title= The Art & Craft of Writing: Favorite Advice for Writers |date= 2015 |publisher= La Favorita Press |isbn= 9781994227050|ignore-isbn-error=true}}

